Class SignatureStore

  • java.lang.Object
    • lz77grammar.SignatureStore
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    class SignatureStore
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    SignatureStore data structure used to convert sequences into unique signatures. Using algorithms discussed In report associated with this project. All functions are discussed in report.
